IMovingAgent, java.io.Serializable, sim.engine.Steppable, sim.portrayal.Portrayal, sim.portrayal.Portrayal2D
public class HiveEntrance
extends AbstractSphericAgent

This class simulates the entrance of a hive. This class will attach itself to the provided hive. Its superclass is AbstractSphericAgent which does all the drawing and the simulation step step(SimState) (nothing).

The constructor for an hive entrance. This constructor calls the constructor of the superclass by providing the entrance's color.

Parameters:
simulation - The simulation where this entrance resides in.
hive - The hive this entrance belongs to.
direction - The direction in degrees where the entrance is located at the outer rim of the hive.
